author: Reuters Editorial
title: New York state overtakes Italy, has coronavirus cases second only to Spain: Reuters tally
description: New York state overtook Italy on Tuesday, reporting overall coronavirus cases second in the world only to Spain, according to a Reuters tally.
content:
(Reuters) - New York state overtook Italy on Tuesday, reporting overall coronavirus cases second in the world only to Spain, according to a Reuters tally.
